{
  "stem": "11179.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Evang-- Evangelical.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They called it evangelist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and they-- I remember one kid in my class, said they called themselves dissidents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Dissidents were agnostics.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They came from, probably, Christian families, but they were agnostics.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't believe in any religion, but they lived-- believed in God.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I guess you call it agnostics here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember only one boy, and people didn't make a big thing out of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The kids did not make a big thing out of it, till-- until they were instigated by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Elementary school was reading, writing, arithmetic, a-- a little bit of geography.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- this is-- you learned to read the map about your neighborhood, and-- and start from then-- from-- from that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then you had art classes, and-- and gym, and music classes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] Though otherwise-- and when I went to-- at ten years, you go to a higher school, which is voluntary.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The school system was-- you could stay eight years in the-- in the elementary school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in-- in the neighborhood I lived, about two-thirds of the kids left, and went to a higher school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went to a school, a 12-year school, [INAUDIBLE] similar to a high school over here, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] geared to-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] to almost any profession you wanted to, but with the exception of medical doctors went to another school where Greek and Latin was required, or one was required, and this school, it was voluntary.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a little easier, maybe, but basically they gave you all the science and so on-- and geography, geology.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Actually, we studied geology, and they gave me foreign languages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I started to learn French when I was 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had French classes.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
